{"type": "article", "id": 36638, "title": "像积木一样把不同口味巧克力搭起来，就成了一份礼物", "description": "有可能因为不是3D打印机直接打印出来的，所以看上去比较好吃？", "date": "2017-01-10T04:35:09Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 544, "name": "巧克力"}, {"id": 2470, "name": "食物设计"}, {"id": 36475, "name": "Universal Favourite"}, {"id": 36611, "name": "Bakedown Cakery"}], "category": 17, "author": 857886, "comment_count": 5, "praise_count": 294, "image": "img/article/article_show/20170110002322qadkrVNsTizF7nCf.jpg", "contents": "<p>3D 打印食品从几年前走入人们视野里开始，就是贴标高科技元素的暗黑料理界新星。但由悉尼独立设计工作室 <a href=\"http://universalfavourite.com.au/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Universal Favourite</a> 联合同城烘焙坊 <a href=\"http://www.bakedowncakery.com/#welcome\" rel=\"nofollow\">Bakedown Cakery</a> 推出的 3D 打印巧克力却不大一样，它们看起来精致、漂亮，更重要的是，那些美好的颜色让人非常想咬一口试试。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170110005124O4JYPl9kFQuWnG8q.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.748000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170110005133KZUGvftcVbhC3NR6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.678667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201701100051469DMQXE1wIYhaL7kG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.711333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>作为一家专注于互动设计、品牌战略和平面设计的独立工作室，2016 年末，Universal Favouraite 想给自己的客户寄去一份有趣的礼物以表感谢。他们找到了同是设计师出身的 Jen Lo 和她的烘培店 Bakedown Cakery，联手创作了名为 <a href=\"https://www.complements.com.au/\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\" rel=\"nofollow\">Complements</a> 的巧克力礼盒。<br></p><p>每块 Complements 巧克力呈现阶梯状，有三个台阶，一上一下两块叠起来就是一个正方形，两块巧克力可以任意组合。Universal Favouraite 设计了这个积木般的形状和巧克力表面的颜色、花纹，并利用 3D 打印机打印出巧克力模具，Bakedown Cakery 则负责创作巧克力的口味。目前，他们开发出了 12 种口味，也许有一种是你喜欢或是好奇的：</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201701100028134XociPdsAT31V2RO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.673333\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">奶油酥饼味</figcaption></figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170110002837WSylpCF5i7O8HX30.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.690667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">黑巧克力味</figcaption></figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170110002844MkSAuIn2CzxiYtNj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.680000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">奶油曲奇味</figcaption></figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170110002852kH6QoBNu9CgchLvl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.660000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">草莓味</figcaption></figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170110003027yk9DdSgVaUl4PoBe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.677333\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">西瓜味</figcaption></figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170110003035r9oLDsIq0OXCHiwZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665333\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">樱桃味</figcaption></figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170110003044NDQYjwfsLCA9mtuE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.652000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">抹茶味</figcaption></figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170110003053IFLXhTS8gq7A3Y40.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.661333\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">开心果味</figcaption></figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170110003101TeEND9XGJCZHrB1g.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.674667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">柠檬味</figcaption></figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170110003113Uo1izbwLIXF92qD0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665333\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">香草味</figcaption></figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170110003126iw9Tr1SgXb8u52hE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.668000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">黑醋栗味</figcaption></figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170110003142nSmRkQMXKjD0i28s.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.664000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">棉花糖味...？</figcaption></figure></div><p class=\"\">每颗巧克力都可以被自由组合、拼搭在一起。<a href=\"https://www.complements.com.au/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Universal Favouraite 表示</a>，他们的灵感源自于“和客户之间所产生的奇妙联系”，从而想要制作出“无限的可能性”。</p><p class=\"\">Complements巧克力的包装盒运用了与巧克力表面相似的花纹。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170110004124Bz5xpZrQ3iUAHtf2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.722000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>除了设计工作室的客户们能够收到这套有趣的巧克力，在 Complements 的官方网站上，Universal Favouraite 还开通了一个“Win a box”通道，用户可以写下自己独创的巧克力口味和创作灵感，如果口味够独特，也许可以为自己赢到一盒限量模块巧克力。不过，目前这个功能只对澳洲的居民开放。</p><p><br></p><p class=\"\">题图及内容中的图片均来自：<a href=\"https://www.complements.com.au/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Complements</a></p>"}